children":[{"type":"text","value":"廠商 惇陽工程顧問有限公司"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主管機關 龜山區公所"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市府資訊查詢: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://web.pcc.gov.tw/tps/atm/AtmAwardWithoutSso/QueryAtmAwardDetail?pkAtmMain=NzA4Mzg1MDU%3D&fbclid=IwY2xjawKdH5BleHRuA2FlbQIxMABicmlkETF1VE1OV2JpSHlBcGtnc0FvAR4Iypwnv0xWgXCI7APxDv0iKI9FmOD5wSu57Qb95HdUuNNILkz7j7TZfCDqkQ_aem_ejqswEBZsjcZKq45ZYziQQ"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"政府電子採購網"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-114-年桃園市龜山長樂公園綠廊串聯計畫"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. 114 年桃園市龜山長樂公園綠廊串聯計畫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長樂公園-綠廊串聯改善工程"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"日期 2026/07/31 舉辦說明會"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提案 李宗豪議員"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 2,600 萬 由中央補助 1,000 萬 已核定"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 規劃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"資訊來源 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.tycc.gov.tw/tc/LiveVideo/video_in.aspx?id=1064"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪議員總質詢"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 2025/05/23 錄影檔 1:35:00"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本案由李宗豪議員提議！將大埔派出所旁閒置地美化。希望增加兒童遊戲設施, 作為新舊社區之間的美化綠帶。本案已經爭取到中央約一千萬的補助款，總額三千萬。相信能有相當不錯的社區公園建設！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地方說明會"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1AvCHrs7kj/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪臉書 2025/07/31:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天召開「樂善里及長樂公園綠廊串連改善工程」地方說明會，感謝鄉親熱情參與。\n這個計畫是宗豪率先提案爭取，也感謝都發局爭取中央補助 1000 萬，計劃總經費約 2600 萬，現在終於一步一步進入實際規劃！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫將樂善國小旁、文德公園、長樂公園一帶零碎的綠地整合，改善內容包含三大方向："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1️⃣ 打造兒童遊戲場域.\n在南北側規劃「冒險型」及「親子型」兩種不同的公園，能探索、攀爬、滑行的動態空間，讓孩子盡情放電；也有沙坑、鞦韆等設施，適合幼齡孩童與親子共玩。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2️⃣ 行人動線優化.\n改善人行路徑，串連學校、公園與社區，讓大家走路更方便安全，也更適合散步、騎 YouBike。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n3️⃣ 夜間照明營造.\n加強燈光設計，晚上也能有舒適安心的環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/174NEPQyuW/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫 臉書 2025/07/31:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未來將會有共融遊戲場、戶外體健區、公園綠廊，同時兼顧樂善國小、文德非營利幼兒園周邊行人空間！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫也在會中再次提出建議，希望能將長慶二街與樂學路交叉口旁的雜木林、長庚集團兩塊私地協調，整理成公園停車空間。這塊空地目前不僅雜草叢生、還常被亂丟垃圾，若能妥善規劃為停車區，不僅改善環境，也能有效收納樂學路上的路側停車，讓整體動線更順暢！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行人更友善、停車更便利，遊具體健更多樣，公園使用體驗會更好！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-23.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-23.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根據圖片上的標示，這項計劃增加的工程項目匯總如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增建遊戲場, 運動設備"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遊戲場 - 冒險型"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：新增一個以冒險為主題的遊戲場。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遊戲場 - 親子型"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：新增一個適合親子共同使用的遊戲場。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體健空間"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：強化運動健康的活動設施。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行人動線優化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文德幼兒園銜接綠廊步道建置 (公園內)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：新建連接文德幼兒園的綠廊步道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停車場增加人本空間"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：在停車場區域，增加以行人為本的空間，改善整體環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善園小旁步道，銜接樂學路人行道拓寬"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：拓寬樂善園小旁的步道，使其與樂學路的人行道相連。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文德二路 86 巷完善無障礙動線"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：改善文德二路 86 巷的動線，使其符合無障礙設施的標準。加強管制違規停車, 確保汽車能雙向通行。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"廣場動線調整"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：調整廣場區域的行進動線。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂學路 622 巷路口改善"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：改善路口處的交通與行人設施。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"交通配套設施"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"YouBike 建置"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：在規劃區域內設置 YouBike 租借站。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爭取長慶二路與樂學路私人土地改建公園停車場"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"綠美化公園, 強化安全措施"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"綠美化涼亭休憩廣場"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：將現有的休憩廣場予以保留並增加植樹，增加灌木群種植, 綠美化公園景觀。。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"綠美化滯水池"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：保留現有的滯水池, 並加強附近植數及綠化， 增加灌木群種植, 綠美化公園景觀。。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"夜間照明營造"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 加強燈光設計，晚上也能有舒適安心的環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"監控設施及電纜地下化"}]},{"type":"text","value":": 整體園區裝置必要的安全監控, 並將所有空中電纜地下化。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"改善說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改善說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本項說明希望能匯總現況的說明， 作為政府改善的參考。希望"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民持續提供意見"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 也希望"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"議員/立委們能參考作為建言的依據"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 是在台地之上, 周圍圍繞著自然保護區的綠色森林。但重劃區仍有許多畸零地, 除了種菜也往往也是雜草重生。對居住環境造成髒亂的毒瘤, 成為蚊蠅蛇鼠的溫床。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回想一下這裡曾經是如此的狀態！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善里-綠廊串連改善"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-11.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-11.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n長慶一街公滯 3 一帶"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-13.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-13.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n樂學路 公 20 公園"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長樂公園-綠廊串聯改善"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-24.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-24.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n長慶二街與樂學路 的私人土地, 目前成為垃圾場。 滋生的蚊蠅是地區毒瘤。 希望市府能依據陳雅倫議員的建議, 建立未來兒童遊戲場/公園旁的停車空間。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-25.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-25.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大埔派出所旁的閒置土地。 在李宗豪議員的爭取下, 將建制"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"冒險型 遊戲場"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 這裡原是櫻花林, 希望能保留及增加 櫻花樹！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-26.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-26.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停車場增加人本空間"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 這停車場中間很寬。 應該建立行人專用道，讓人車分離。 目前是停車前 30 分鐘免費，但極少人利用。 希望能讓文德二路 86 巷能嚴格取締違停車輛， 讓該路段汽車能雙向通行。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-27.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-27.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這個輪椅/嬰兒車的無障礙人行道 已經成為機車通行道。 希望能建制 輪椅/嬰兒車專用閘門, 防止機車/自行車通行！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-28.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-28.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂學路 622 巷路口改善"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 這路口將做改善, 應該讓外出車輛都右轉進入 文德二路 128 巷。 返回社區車輛都需走 文光路單行道。 兩車道是否能考慮分離，直接對應到巷道？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-29.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-29.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這裡將是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"親子型 遊戲場"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 將會有哪些設施呢？ 居民只能期盼 還是能提出建議？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"施工進展-及-議員們的努力"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"施工進展 及 議員們的努力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善里-綠廊串連改善"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-3.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-2.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長樂公園-綠廊串聯改善"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這些畸零地其實可以成為社區旁的小公園, 有著讓您驚喜的花園綠地。早晨可以在此看日出, 觀賞無限景觀森林。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025/05 改善工程開始架設圍籬！可望 2026 年初給樂善國小生活圈的居民一個驚喜的特色景觀。 也希望居民能於 2026 民意調查時給市府在"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"整頓市容"}]},{"type":"text","value":"項目一個滿意的讚！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025/07/18 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1Ym78wWrd9/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李宗豪臉書"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n宗豪成功爭取千萬補助 「樂善里綠廊串聯改善工程」！\n今天再次邀集在地居民、樂善國小、里長與區公所等單位，一起討論未來的設計方向，希望整體規劃能更貼近在地的需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"過去這條綠廊因為規劃零碎、空間閒置，長期無法發揮它的功能與價值。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"宗豪持續關心這個案子，不僅在議會質詢，也多次到現場會勘，並成功爭取中央補助經費 1050 萬元，未來將整理樂善國小周邊綠帶，整合文德公園與長樂公園，打通新舊社區的生活動線，也會增設更完整的兒童遊戲區和停車空間，讓孩子有地方奔跑、家長有地方休憩、居民有空間交流"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c48-21.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c48-21.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025/06/05: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/19GFzA69Lu/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫 臉書"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫建請市府解決下面問題！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"✅ 建議開闢「公 20 公園」旁未利用的 147 地號綠地，設置公園附屬停車場與兒童遊戲區。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 要求用都發基金取得長慶二街與樂學路口的閒置綠地，現況綠地內雜林及垃圾一堆，整理後整合文德、長樂公園，打造完整的公園遊戲場及停車空間。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4090-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4090-4.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},